Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:41.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(500,500)}本字幕由豌豆字幕組&風之聖殿字幕組聯合製作 \N僅供學習交流 禁止用於商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:10.03,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:23.54,oped,,0,0,0,,初出茅廬的我 面對充滿未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:35.30,oped,,0,0,0,,像那一天一色的晨空般 無數次驚訝不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:45.98,oped,,0,0,0,,現在正鐫刻歷史 胸中也滿溢思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:51.57,oped,,0,0,0,,定能創造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:58.16,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:03.79,oped,,0,0,0,,一切都光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:09.29,oped,,0,0,0,,不為人知的自己 發現未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:24.56,oped,,0,0,0,,我不懈追尋 那最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.23,oped,,0,0,0,,永不停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.59,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,發生奇蹟的機率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.57,oped,,0,0,0,,根本無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.07,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.16,oped,,0,0,0,,或許只是神明的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.30,oped,,0,0,0,,明天的天空會是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:32.09,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們去看看 那未知的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:39.27,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:44.65,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.40,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:55.99,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情…或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.54,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,262)}那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.67,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天是愉快的星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來做便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來做雞蛋卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}把雞蛋打好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}打蛋打蛋打雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在鍋裡滿滿地塗一層油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}四角也要塗滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}往滾燙的鍋裡倒雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}從下往上卷卷卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卷卷卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再塗一層油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}塗塗塗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再倒一點雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}從下往上卷卷卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卷卷卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:26.16,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和彩虹和曾祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望能好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒問題的 你這麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小鬼也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}天氣好像也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}適合約會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}約 約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不就是約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}兩個人出門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是約會還能是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你 你和雪兔哥的份 我放到便當盒裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你要好好在雪兔哥家幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你一個人去幫他打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不要只知道玩 別給他添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有比我更適合幫忙打掃衛生的封印獸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道 我認識的封印獸只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}幹得漂亮 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}時間也剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不准偷吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 不好意思 這裡是木之本家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是誰想偷吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是圓美阿姨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是我 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在方便說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}其實 我今天突然接到電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一聲不響 偷偷摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你外公嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是媽媽的爺爺 也就是我的曾祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}剛才知世的媽媽打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說是他有個東西一定要在今天給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他好像明天要出國辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好幾個月才能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明都和你約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 這是很重要的事吧 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦 是知世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我這裡也是大道寺發來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在這裡可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}門鈴在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是木之本櫻小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}恭候多時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼 你好像習慣了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明就有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 你家也有管家來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 偉就像家人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天突然叫你來 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你明天就要出國了 這麼忙還叫我過來 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為我有個東西一定要交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在此之前 能給我介紹一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他叫李小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他和我在同一個國中 同一個年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在隔壁班 是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫李小狼 謝謝您的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學 今天打亂了你們的安排 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我聽說你們原本打算一起出去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是小櫻做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看起來好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 你們原本不是要兩個人一起吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家一起吃才更美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有這個 也請嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個也很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼廚藝很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你做的菜更好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒這回事 你做的點心才更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 你的更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你的更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也就是說 你們做的菜都很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}兩位的拿手菜 我就來嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這茶好好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是我上次出差的時候買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我覺得你應該會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻他們應該已經見到曾祖父了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爺爺也真是的 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是有東西想交給小櫻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 為什麼要李同學也一起去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那當然 畢竟他是和小櫻一起出去玩的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爺爺肯定是想見見他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學一定能讓真嬉曾祖父滿意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}多謝款待 真的很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去倒茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是去那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 找裡面的人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就說你想再要一壺茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你單獨和我一起還是會緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事沒事 我也失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能陪我聊聊天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}您不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻在學校怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一直都笑容滿面 很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只要看著她 大家都感到很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻的母親也和她一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爺爺 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你看 彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她一直都笑容滿面 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家只要看著她 就覺得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過有一點和小櫻不同 她不擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你看 我沒有壓到花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她真的很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是 這麼溫柔的孩子 我卻讓她傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}都怪我意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在她最幸福的時候 沒有去祝福她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還沒來得及道歉 她就離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 我見到了小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看到小櫻 就好像再次看到了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也終於有機會 和我一直疏遠的人 和她心愛的人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我不了解情況 說這種話或許不太合適
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我覺得您孫女一定也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}撫子也好 小櫻也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們把我心愛的孩子從我身邊搶走 真是可恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 您剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我在說 人生不可能事事順心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔 你不打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}桃矢演怪人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真勤勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他說想要自己解決學費
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 還想幫助小櫻上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}或者支持她做想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是個好哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然說話難聽了點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟他是個資深妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道我幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但即便如此 我也會為小櫻和大家而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請幫我轉達給另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}月 你聽到了吧 不用我再說一遍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}桃矢哥哥的力量也回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 小櫻的力量變得無比強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這兩者不可能無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和英國聯繫上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發來了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有誰能幫我倒壺茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到這種地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是媽媽的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}將這裡的過去放映出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「記錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不可以再繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是再繼續下去 會回不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又是這個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你怎麼了 不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我聽見了時鐘的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有一個穿著長袍的人站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那件長袍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒錯 是我們家族代代傳承的正裝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是我的長袍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}安心地睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你一直沒回來 我就和李同學來找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去叫醫生來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只是有點頭暈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:20:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}開始同步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看見了和卡牌製作者同樣的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}書的內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}更新了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢的力量越來越強了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是不是比預想的快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}並沒有很快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那邊的守護者注意到了 已經開始有所行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好久不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可魯貝洛斯 月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還不是因為你一直不回信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們可是很生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我看出來了 特別是看到月的表情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}用魔法陣的圖像叫來我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你終於打算說出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就解釋一下這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我主人身上發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}最擔心的事 即將變成現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}話說這句台詞也熟練了很多 這裡是「交給小可」環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次要介紹的是 在曾祖父的別墅中吃過的便當和點心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}首先是小櫻的便當 我和雪兔也吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她一直在練習 雞蛋卷已經成了極品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}炸雞塊 炸肉餅 炒蔬菜 醋拌涼菜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也考慮到了營養的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後是小鬼做的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:31.24,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次我也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好久沒有見到曾祖父 還是那麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}話說他的別墅好大啊 還有好幾棟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.34,0:24:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也想在避暑地的別墅裡喝冷飲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.11,0:24:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}曾祖父開車把我送回家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到家後總覺得有些不對勁
